## 20. Admin Workflow Integration

The Google Cloud AI subsystem should fit into the admin document workflow, not operate as a detached lab experiment.

## 20.1 Current workflow

1. admin opens document form
2. admin uploads file
3. admin clicks generate description
4. result is inserted into the description field

