5. gateway invokes Vertex AI
6. result returns to the app
7. app updates job status and displays output
8. admin can accept, edit, or regenerate
9. final approved value is written to the document record

## 20.3 UI states to support

- idle
- validating
- generating
- success
- failed
- regenerated
- manually overridden

