You will want visibility into what the AI layer is doing before it becomes a mystery tax.

## 21.1 Structured logs to capture

| Field | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `feature` | document description, metadata, summary |
| `documentId` | related entity |
| `requestedBy` | admin identity |
| `status` | success/failure |
| `model` | model used |
| `latencyMs` | performance |
| `inputMimeType` | diagnostics |
| `inputSizeBytes` | diagnostics and cost awareness |
| `errorCode` | failure analysis |
