## 21.2 Monitoring metrics to track

- success rate
- failure rate
- median latency
- p95 latency
- requests by feature
- requests by environment
- manual override rate
- regenerate rate

## 21.3 Why this matters

If admins regenerate everything or rewrite all outputs, the issue is likely your prompt, preprocessing, or model choice. The logs should make that obvious instead of forcing everyone into ritual guesswork.

